This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new algorithm for extreme multi-label classification. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as multi-label classification is often used in information retrieval tasks. Additionally, the paper mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are both sub-categories of CS. Finally, the paper's focus on improving prediction accuracy suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
